00:06:57.122 --> 00:06:59.067
Ngomong-ngomong, dimana Ambika?

00:06:59.569 --> 00:07:02.140
Sebenarnya, dia tidak bisa hadir.
Dia akan datang nanti.

00:07:02.469 --> 00:07:05.612
